name: Colorful Michael Jackson
description: We designed 30,000 sets of personalized clothing for Michael Jackson and cast them into NFT,Each set is unique,We collected for 6 years,Finally, the different design patterns are displayed through AI technology,In the future, we will create a meta-universe through NFT,Design the special art assets of the meta-universe world.In the future,We may decide more activities in the form of DAO,For example, hold a 3D concert for Mike Jackson.
